.TH "cm_opa_to_ib_sgid" 9 "cm_opa_to_ib_sgid" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
cm_opa_to_ib_sgid \- Convert OPA SGID to IB SGID ULPs (such as IPoIB) do not understand OPA GIDs and will reject them as the local_gid will not match the sgid. Therefore, change the pathrec's SGID to an IB SGID.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" cm_opa_to_ib_sgid
.BI "(struct cm_work *work "  ","
.BI "struct sa_path_rec *path "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "work" 12
Work completion
.IP "path" 12
Path record
